'''美人鱼综合症'''（{{lang-en|'''Sirenomelia'''}} 或 '''Mermaid Syndrome'''）是一种非常罕见的先天性缺陷，两条腿融合在一起，看起来像“[[美人鱼|美人鱼]]”。估计在大约十万个新生儿中会有一例<ref name=jmg>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?cmd=Retrieve&db=pubmed&dopt=Abstract&list_uids=1552541 PubMed PMID: 1552541]</ref>（与[[连体双胞胎|连体双胞胎]]機率相当）。婴儿通常因为并发[[肾脏|肾脏]]和[[膀胱|膀胱]]异常，会在出生后一两天内死亡。约有一半的美人鱼综合征病例都会胎死腹中，并且这种缺陷在[[同卵双胞胎|同卵双胞胎]]发生的機率要高于非双胞胎和[[异卵双胞胎|异卵双胞胎]]的100倍。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aolhealth.com/health/mermaid-syndrome-sirenomelia|title="Shiloh Pepin: The Mermaid Girl"|author=Mary Beth Sammons|access-date=2012-08-30|archive-date=2009-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091125232234/http://www.aolhealth.com/health/mermaid-syndrome-sirenomelia|dead-url=no}}</ref>目前，利用外科手术可以将融合的下肢，或融合的内脏分离<ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=pubmed&Cmd=ShowDetailView&TermToSearch=16801393 PubMed PMID: 16801393]</ref>。实验证明{{le|骨形成蛋白-7|Bone morphogenetic protein 7}}可能在此疾病的发病中起作用<ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=pubmed&Cmd=ShowDetailView&TermToSearch=15843411 Zakin L, et al., Sirenomelia in Bmp7 and Tsg compound mutant mice: requirement for Bmp signaling in the development of ventral posterior mesoderm.  Development. 2005 May;132(10):2489 PMID: 15843411]</ref>.

